As the temperatures drop, thoughts are turning to our winter wardrobe and if you're looking for some serious seasonal style inspiration, look no further than Michelle Keegan's new range for Lipsy.

The actress-turned-designer is back with her festive collection and it's full of faux furs, cosy knits and stylish coats.

Speaking to MailOnline about her new range, which lands tomorrow, Michelle said: 'I love winter - Christmas is my favourite time of year so I couldn’t wait to get back into the design room to create some classic winter pieces.

